headline: Deere Could Outperform Peers Near-Term Amid Agriculture Downturn, Morgan Stanley Says
summary: Deere (DE) could outperform its peers in the near term during the agriculture downturn after it posted a fiscal Q4 beat and issued a below-consensus fiscal 2025 guidance, Morgan Stanley said in a note Monday.
